data.text: Tiatr Academy of Goa has its headquarters in Margao, Goa, India. This blog is a collection of news items of tiatr, Konkani music albums, VCDs, films and related to the tiatr fraternity and is a personal attempt to archive the same. Where possible we have provided the links/original source. Any comments made by the writer of the articles is solely their point of view. http://welcometoindia.com/vidfeeder_view.php?id=dbuTOUb4-YM Gaspar Almeida www.goa-world.com
